{"tid":1393880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[不合作運動] 集體交多少少稅有冇得諗？","createTime":"2019-08-01T08:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T10:52:41.000Z","uid":291805,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"123a7916704c8cf584aa26cb686e0c4a3392afe2","tid":1393880,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:34:03.000Z","msg":"唔好閙狗我住，我都極度唔Ｌ想交稅俾呢個濕鳩無恥既政府。<br />\n可惜，集體唔交稅屬於犯法，連遲交都會被罰款，無謂益佢。<br />\n純粹以不合作運動，增加政府營運成本既角度去睇，每人多交＄7.77得唔得？<br />\n如果100萬人都多交$7.77，佢地淨係退稅都要出100萬張支票，你都咪話唔仆街。<br />\n大家點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pjEDF1N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpjEDF1N.png&h=ae486adf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/tax/refundchq.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ird.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Ftax%2Frefundchq.htm&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl53HDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=92463872\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/tax/refundchq.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>退還稅款</strong><br />\n<strong>如有多繳稅款，稅務局會以支票形式退還給你。</strong>退款支票會以平郵寄往你最後提供的通訊地址。若通訊地址有所更改，你應盡早通知稅務局，以免延誤。<br />\n<br />\n退款支票須於支票發出日期 6 個月內存入你的銀行戶口。逾期未領的款項可用作抵銷你應付的稅款。"},{"pid":"e4fd6eb36b10cbfd782a6f2b7727b41017067578","tid":1393880,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:42:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c19ad60a2692d5a6466b2d28ba0c48ac669d8eee","tid":1393880,"uid":118623,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:43:21.000Z","msg":"諗多咗"},{"pid":"55baff2ea9fd60b0c6eab66cd952d1cda6687090","tid":1393880,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:43:47.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"5c0e2763a704e73cc030ff61b98a8139b483ed0b","tid":1393880,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:44:07.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------<br />\n[極重要] 聽日開始全民查閱選民登記冊<br />\n<a